snippet.title: Micro Annihilation Teaser
snippet.description:
🎮 Buy now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1510890/Micro_Annihilation
💬 Join the Discord, shape the future! https://discord.gg/AMTKx9R

Micro Annihilation is a real-time strategy, inspired by classics such as Command & Conquer, where your battlefields are inside homes, offices, and everything in between. Airlift troops onto the dining room table, launch artillery across the bedroom, and bring down the house while waging war upon a new mysterious foe.

#RTS​ #StrategyGame #Gaming
